    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a persistent misfire and several noticeable fluid leaks that need immediate attention. Cosmetically, the exterior shows its age with faded paint, several dents, and surface rust in multiple areas. The interior also requires a complete overhaul, as the upholstery is heavily worn and some electronic components are non-functional. It is currently not in reliable driving condition and will likely need to be towed.",
